{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1787,"text":"I was sitting with my girls,"},{"time":4780,"text":"and Joy said,"},{"time":6293,"text":"\"Dang, I wish he'd get off my back."},{"time":10271,"text":"My daddy, he calls me all the time.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":14127,"text":"\"Lucky for you he calls at all,\" said Jasmine."},{"time":17393,"text":"\"I haven't heard from my dad in years.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":21053,"text":"At this moment, I knew the girls needed a way"},{"time":25285,"text":"to connect with their fathers."},{"time":27862,"text":"At Camp Diva, my non-profit organization,"},{"time":31625,"text":"we have these types of conversations all the time"},{"time":35162,"text":"as a way to help girls of African descent"},{"time":38354,"text":"prepare for their passage into womanhood."},{"time":41936,"text":"These girls just needed"},{"time":45477,"text":"a way to invite their fathers into their lives"},{"time":49318,"text":"on their own terms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52015,"text":"So I asked the girls,"},{"time":53468,"text":"\"How can we help other girls"},{"time":56604,"text":"develop healthy relationships with their fathers?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":60894,"text":"\"Let's have a dance,\" one girl shouted,"},{"time":65397,"text":"and all the girls quickly backed her up."},{"time":69730,"text":"They started dreaming about the decorations,"},{"time":72636,"text":"invitations, the dresses they were going to wear,"},{"time":76050,"text":"and what their fathers could and could not wear. (Laughter)"},{"time":80196,"text":"It was off and running before I could even blink my eyes,"},{"time":84767,"text":"but even if I could have slowed down those girls,"},{"time":88837,"text":"I wouldn't have,"},{"time":90177,"text":"because one thing that I have learned"},{"time":92258,"text":"from over a decade of working with girls"},{"time":95336,"text":"is that they already know what they need."},{"time":98856,"text":"The wisdom lives inside of them."},{"time":103533,"text":"As long as they have infrastructure,"},{"time":106181,"text":"mentorship and resources,"},{"time":108597,"text":"they can build what they need,"},{"time":112015,"text":"not only to survive, but to thrive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117449,"text":"So we had a dance,"},{"time":121673,"text":"and girls and their fathers came in multitudes."},{"time":126213,"text":"They were dressed to the nines."},{"time":129188,"text":"They acted sweet."},{"time":131431,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":135117,"text":"They acted silly."},{"time":136967,"text":"They really enjoyed each other's company."},{"time":140188,"text":"It was a huge success."},{"time":143029,"text":"And the girls decided to make it an annual event."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148240,"text":"So as the seasons changed,"},{"time":150832,"text":"and it was time to plan the dance again,"},{"time":153552,"text":"one girl named Brianna spoke up,"},{"time":156659,"text":"and she said,"},{"time":158849,"text":"\"My dad can't come to the dance,"},{"time":161595,"text":"and this whole thing is making me sad.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":165832,"text":"\"Why not?\" the girls asked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168840,"text":"\"Because he's in jail,\" she bravely admitted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173520,"text":"\"Well, can he just get out for a day?\" one of the girls asked. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178454,"text":"\"And come in shackles?"},{"time":181632,"text":"That's worse than not having him here at all.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":185977,"text":"At this moment, I saw an opportunity"},{"time":190395,"text":"for the girls to rise to the occasion"},{"time":193321,"text":"and to become their own heroes."},{"time":196085,"text":"So I asked, \"What do you think we should do about this?"},{"time":200758,"text":"We want every girl to experience the dance, right?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":206008,"text":"So the girls thought for a moment,"},{"time":207671,"text":"and one girl suggested,"},{"time":209980,"text":"\"Why don't we just take the dance in the jail?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":214286,"text":"Most of the girls doubted the possibility of that,"},{"time":218102,"text":"and said, \"Are you crazy?"},{"time":220896,"text":"Who is going to allow a bunch of little girls,"},{"time":223904,"text":"dressed up — \" (Laughter)"},{"time":226368,"text":"\" — to come inside a jail and dance with their daddies in Spongebob suits?\""},{"time":231955,"text":"Because that's what they called them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235303,"text":"I said, \"Girls, well, well,"},{"time":239461,"text":"you never know unless you ask.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":243464,"text":"So a letter was written to the Richmond City Sheriff,"},{"time":247904,"text":"signed collectively by each girl,"},{"time":251723,"text":"and I would have to say, he is a very special sheriff."},{"time":257129,"text":"He contacted me immediately and said,"},{"time":262062,"text":"whenever there is an opportunity to bring families inside,"},{"time":268016,"text":"his doors are always open."},{"time":271188,"text":"Because one thing he did know,"},{"time":273513,"text":"that when fathers are connected to their children,"},{"time":276840,"text":"it is less likely that they will return."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281803,"text":"So,"},{"time":283884,"text":"16 inmates and 18 girls were invited."},{"time":289738,"text":"The girls were dressed in their Sunday best,"},{"time":293387,"text":"and the fathers traded in their yellow and blue jumpsuits"},{"time":298416,"text":"for shirts and ties."},{"time":302920,"text":"They hugged."},{"time":305291,"text":"They shared a full catered meal of chicken and fish."},{"time":310042,"text":"They laughed together."},{"time":313767,"text":"It was beautiful."},{"time":318175,"text":"The fathers and daughters even experienced"},{"time":322416,"text":"an opportunity to have a physical connection,"},{"time":326491,"text":"something that a lot of them didn't even have"},{"time":329220,"text":"for a while."},{"time":330452,"text":"Fathers were in a space where they were able to"},{"time":334863,"text":"make their daughters play,"},{"time":337576,"text":"and pull out her chair and extend his hand for a dance."},{"time":343825,"text":"Even the guards cried."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347502,"text":"But after the dance,"},{"time":350222,"text":"we all realized that Dad still would be in jail."},{"time":355782,"text":"So we needed to create something"},{"time":358875,"text":"that they could take with them."},{"time":360633,"text":"So we brought in Flip cams,"},{"time":363248,"text":"and we had them look at the Flip cams"},{"time":365989,"text":"and just interview each other --"},{"time":367717,"text":"their messages, their thoughts."},{"time":371431,"text":"This was going to be used as a touchstone"},{"time":374614,"text":"so when they started to miss each other"},{"time":377030,"text":"and feel disconnected,"},{"time":379330,"text":"they could reconnect through this image."}]},{"cues":[{"time":382694,"text":"I'll never forget that one girl looked in her father's eyes"},{"time":388076,"text":"with that camera and said,"},{"time":389396,"text":"\"Daddy, when you look at me, what do you see?\""},{"time":396106,"text":"Because our daddies are our mirrors"},{"time":400194,"text":"that we reflect back on"},{"time":402616,"text":"when we decide about what type of man we deserve,"},{"time":407386,"text":"and how they see us for the rest of our lives."},{"time":410977,"text":"I know that very well,"},{"time":414522,"text":"because I was one of the lucky girls."},{"time":416923,"text":"I have had"},{"time":422798,"text":"my father in my life always."},{"time":428805,"text":"He's even here today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430685,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":439722,"text":"And that is why it is extremely special"},{"time":443700,"text":"for me to make sure that these girls"},{"time":446944,"text":"are connected to their fathers,"},{"time":449474,"text":"especially those who are separated"},{"time":452383,"text":"because of barbed wires and metal doors."},{"time":457269,"text":"We have just created a form"},{"time":460362,"text":"for girls who have heavy questions on their heart"},{"time":463745,"text":"to be in a position to ask their fathers those questions"},{"time":468237,"text":"and given the fathers the freedom to answer."},{"time":473004,"text":"Because we know that the fathers"},{"time":476349,"text":"are even leaving with this one thought:"},{"time":479597,"text":"What type of woman am I preparing to put in the world?"},{"time":484966,"text":"Because a father is locked in"},{"time":488383,"text":"does not mean he should be locked out"},{"time":491433,"text":"of his daughter's life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493984,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}